public class LookupBlockingFifoQueue<V>
extends java.util.AbstractQueue<V>
implements java.util.concurrent.BlockingQueue<V>

A O(1) blocking linked list implementation. Backed by a linked hash map to allow O(1) removal of and membedrship checks.
